kɨɨntʉ kɨlʉme na va kɨɨntʉ kiki.
Arɨfakisáadi akafiiíkye myaaka makumi yatatʉ nɨ ɨsaano,
Arɨfakisáadi akamʉvyáale Séela, akkala myaaka magana yánɨ nɨ ɨtatʉ. Mpɨɨndɨ ijo, ajáa aava na vaana
akamʉvyaala Séela.  va kɨɨntʉ kɨlʉme na va kɨɨntʉ kiki.
Séela akafiiíkye myaaka makumi yatatʉ, akamʉvyaala Ebéeri.
Séela akamʉvyáale Ebéeri, akkala myaaka magana yánɨ nɨ ɨtatʉ
. Mpɨɨndɨ ijo, ajáa aava na vaana vɨɨngɨ va kɨɨntʉ kɨlʉme na va kɨɨntʉ kiki.
Ebéeri akafiiíkye myaaka makumi yatatʉ nɨ ɨne, akamʉvyaala
Peléegi.   
Ebéeri akamʉvyáale Peléegi, akkala myaaka magana
yánɨ na makumi yatatʉ. Mpɨɨndɨ ijo, ajáa aava na vaana va
kɨɨntʉ kɨlʉme na va kɨɨntʉ kiki.
Peléegi akafiiíkye myaaka makumi yatatʉ, akamʉvyaala Réeu. Peléegi akamʉvyáale Réeu, akkala myaaka magana yavɨrɨ na keenda. Mpɨɨndɨ ijo, ajáa aava na vaana va kɨɨntʉ kɨlʉme na
va kɨɨntʉ kiki.
Réeu akafiiíkye myaaka makumi yatatʉ nɨ ɨvɨrɨ, akamʉvyaala
Serúugi. 
Réeu akamʉvyáale Serúugi akkala myaaka magana
yavɨrɨ na mufúngatɨ. Mpɨɨndɨ ijo, ajáa aava na vaana va kɨɨntʉ
kɨlʉme na va kɨɨntʉ kiki.
Serúugi akafiiíkye myaaka makumi yatatʉ, akamʉvyaala
Nahóori. 
Serúugi akamʉvyáale Nahóori, akkala myaaka magana
yavɨrɨ. Mpɨɨndɨ ijo, ajáa aava na vaana va kɨɨntʉ kɨlʉme na va
kɨɨntʉ kiki.
Nahóori akafiiíkye myaaka makumi yavɨrɨ na keenda,
akamʉvyaala Téera. 
Nahóori akamʉvyáale Téera, akkala
myaaka igana rɨmwɨ ni ikimi na keenda. Mpɨɨndɨ ijo, ajáa aava na vaana va kɨɨntʉ kɨlʉme na va kɨɨntʉ kiki.
Téera akafiiíkye myaaka makumi mufúngatɨ, akamʉvyaala
Aburáamu,  Nahóori na Haráani.
Vaana va Téera
o
Aya noo masáare ya Téera. Vaana va Téera nɨ Aburáamu, Haráani ajáa awulala kati taáta waavo ajáa akaarɨ kaláa
Nahóori na Haráani. Haráani noo ajáa taáta waala Lúutu.
