Baa kei vajáa
Mweenevyóósi ajáa.  Melikɨsedéeki akamʉtalarya Aburáamu yoosea,
“Ijʉva Mweenevyóósi, Mʉʉmba kurumu nɨ ɨsɨ, amʉtalarye Aburáamu.
