Isaka. i 
Isaka akafiiíkye sikʉ ináanɨ, Aburaháamu akamʉwyɨɨrya
Isaka ajáa Sáara ne akasea, “Mʉlʉʉngʉ ampɨ́ɨre lʉseko. Kɨra mʉʉntʉ
mweene arɨ teera masáare aya, vyeenda arɨ na nɨɨ́nɨ.” 
Akasea,
“Ani ngaarɨ amʉsea Aburaháamu, kʉmwoonkerya ndɨrɨ vaana? Háaha namʉvyáarɨɨre Aburaháamu mwaana wa kɨɨntʉ kɨlʉme
na yeéye ntɨ adalahɨɨre.”
Isaka akakʉla, akadaaniwa koonka. Sikʉ adáanwe,
Aburaháamu ajáa abweeyya ngovi nkʉ́ʉ́lʉ.
Hájiri na Ishimaéeli vookibiriwa
