	Yooséefu kaay kwa Pótifa
Háaha kʉra, a Yooséefu akatwaalwa na Mísiri nɨ
vara Vshimaéeli. Ʉko, Yooséefu akavawa iyoombe kwa Mʉmísiri ʉmwi asewáa Pótifa. Ʉhʉ Pótifa nɨ mʉkʉ́ʉ́lʉ
wa vanyaampála va Faráao ajáa. 
