de mʉndooklaanga vii aha?  sa tʉhone njala yi imalo.”
Vaánaavo na Yooséefu voomwnamɨra Yooséefu 
Sa jeiyo, vaánaavo na
Yooséefu ikimi, vakagirita na
Mísiri noo wʉla viryo. 
Maa
kaa, Yaakúupu si amʉrekera Bénjamini mudúúdi wa Yooséefu adome na vaánaavo na
Mísiri tʉkʉ, sa ajáa ririkana, akasea, “Ha koonɨ irema ramʉfʉmɨɨre mwaana waanɨ
joolɨ ndɨrɨ bweeyya?” 
Jeiyo,
vaana vi Isiraéeli vakafika Mísiri, novo vakava nɨ vamwɨ
va vaantʉ vɨɨtáa noo wʉla viryo, sa baa ɨsɨ ya Kanáani noyo ɨjáa yakwáatirwe nɨ njala yi imalo.
Háaha, Yooséefu noo ajáa
mwmiriri mʉkʉ́ʉ́lʉ wɨ ɨsɨ ya Mísiri. Na yeéye noo mweene avawʉsiráa vaantʉ vóósi viryo.
Vaánaavo na Yooséefu vakafiiíke, maa vakamwnamɨra Yooséefu
Yooséefu akavoona vaánaavo, maa akavataanga. Maa kaa, akbweyya ja sɨ avamanyire, maa akavuurya na nkerʉnkerʉ yoosea, “Hai mʉfúmire ta nyuúnyu?” Novo vakamʉsea, “Tafúmire ɨsɨ ya Kanáani, tʉ́ʉjire noo wʉla viryo.”
fʉʉrʉ ɨsɨ. 
