	Yooséefu nɨ mʉsabií bʉ ʉtʉ́ʉngaa tʉ́ʉngaa, mʉsabií bʉ ʉtʉ́ʉngaa ʉrɨ mbarɨ mbarɨ ya mpula ya maaji, na matáampi yááchwe yakʉ́nɨkɨrɨraa lʉkaande.
Vavɨ vááchwe vamʉvundukirya nkoondo mʉnʉmʉʉnʉ, vamʉlasa na vamʉturikirya.
Maa kaa, ʉta wááchwe wahɨɨndwa nga, na mɨkono yaachwe yatɨɨte ngururu yoo yerera,
sa lʉvɨro lwa Mweene Ngururu wa Yaakúupu, kwa njɨra ya Muriísi na Mwaalaliwye wi Isiraéeli.  Mʉlʉʉngʉ wa vala taáta waanyu kwaambirirya arɨ,
Mʉlʉʉngʉ Mweene Ngururu, kʉtalarya arɨ, na ntalarya ja kurumw, mpula ja maaji yarɨ ɨsɨ,
na vaana varɨ foo na nchuo jiri foo.  Ntalarya ja taáta waanyu nɨ nkʉ́ʉ́lʉ kʉlookya ntalarya
fuma njʉʉlʉ ja sikʉ jóósi, na nɨ nkʉ́ʉ́lʉ kʉlookya viduunda vya sikʉ jóósi.
Ntalarya ijo jive mweeri ya Yooséefu, jive mweeri ya ʉhʉ nuririwa nɨ vaánaavo.
Bénjamini nɨ ja mbʉʉjɨ nkarɨ, namʉtoondo yarijáa ʉsákaati wááchwe,
nwʉlo yagávaa viintʉ vikwáatirwe nkoondwii.” Ava noo ncholo ya nkolo ju ufumo wa vaantʉ vi Isiraéeli. Ayo noo masáare taáta waavo avawyɨɨra mpɨɨndɨ avalairiryáa.
